# Delivery Strict Lite

## Pre-Check
- Clarify objective and scope in one short block.
- List impacted files/modules before editing.
- State planned verification (lint/test/build) briefly.

## Implementation
- Keep changes focused and small.
- Preserve architecture boundaries.
- Do not introduce unrelated refactors.

## Verification
- Run lint checks for touched files.
- Run the most relevant test command when feasible.
- If tests are skipped, state why and what to run next.

## Reporting
- List changed files grouped by Backend/Frontend/DevOps.
- Summarize what was verified and what remains.
